item.title: Information
item.description:
Thanks for checking out my site. This is an assortment of projects and experiments I’ve worked on over the past few years.

I am 21 years old and currently living in New York. My interests primarily involve computers, and are focused on multimedia technologies, networking, information theory, and machine learning. I make weekly attempts with my friends to curate the information overload.
